# CodeShield ignore patterns (gitignore-style).
# Files listed here are excluded from aegisq scans.

# Test fixtures intentionally contain vulnerable string literals
# (eval(...), Math.random(), crypto.createHash("md5"), etc.) used to
# assert the matching rules fire. These are bait, not real vulns.
src/test/**

